### Create History
POST http://localhost:3000/history
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicName": "Dr. García",
  "paramedicName": "Enfermera López",
  "dateAttention": "2023-12-08T10:30:00.000Z",
  "symptoms": "Dolor de cabeza, fiebre y malestar general",
  "observations": "Paciente presenta síntomas gripales",
  "medicines": "Paracetamol 500mg cada 8 horas, Ibuprofeno 400mg cada 12 horas",
  "diagnostic": "Síndrome gripal",
  "patientId": 2
}

### Get All Histories
GET http://localhost:3000/history

### Get History by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/history/1

### Get Histories by Patient ID
GET http://localhost:3000/history/patient/2

### Get Histories with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/history/page?page=1&limit=5

### Update History
PUT http://localhost:3000/history/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "medicName": "Dr. García Actualizado",
  "observations": "Paciente presenta mejoría en los síntomas",
  "medicines": "Paracetamol 500mg cada 12 horas"
}

### Delete History (Soft Delete)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/history/1
